data.name: Debug_CleanEnvStartup
data.value:
Welcome to the clean environment debug mode, it's nice to see you here!
In this mode, all of the settings (app settings, activities, etc.) are deleted each time the main form is launched, that is, each time that SplashScreen.Load occurs.
If you're testing a translations set, you might not want the language to go back to defaults. To prevent such behavior, make sure that you're building with the following constants defined: DEBUG, DEBUG_CLEAN=True and KEEP_LANG=True.
